Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.34,0:00:12.03,Italics,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing. It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.56,0:00:33.49,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Touko!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.96,0:00:34.89,Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.89,0:00:35.80,Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Onee-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.41,0:00:37.59,Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,Touko-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.41,0:00:37.59,Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,Touko?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.69,0:00:50.81,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.09,0:00:56.02,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get them.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.64,0:01:00.81,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.84,0:01:09.03,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,It's my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.03,0:01:15.22,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,No, I asked to watch your \Nmom play piano, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.73,0:01:18.18,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't hear anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.18,0:01:21.98,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,But you felt something strong \Nenough to make you pass out.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.98,0:01:24.28,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,So the experiment was a success?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.28,0:01:25.23,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.89,0:01:29.69,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,But I might have put you in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.88,0:01:32.85,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine. Besides—
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.44,0:01:38.86,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Whenever I try to stay in one place,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.86,0:01:41.40,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I get other people mixed up in my problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.69,0:01:44.79,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Touko,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.31,0:01:48.47,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.47,0:01:50.87,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I want to stay here a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.60,0:01:53.48,Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,O-Onee-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.48,0:01:57.31,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,You're right. You should \Nstay put a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.31,0:01:59.93,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I want to make beads when I get home.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.93,0:02:01.01,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.19,0:02:13.73,Episode-Title - Copy - Copy,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,264)}Final Episode:\N"Shooting Star"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.48,0:02:17.97,Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure we should \Nhave left Onee-chan there?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.97,0:02:19.15,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.41,0:02:22.24,Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what happened to her, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.24,0:02:23.89,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.30,0:02:26.41,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,She's getting to that age.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.71,0:02:29.98,Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,What? Are you saying I'm the only kid here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.98,0:02:32.21,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,You're almost an adult, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.21,0:02:33.75,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll happen before you know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.09,0:02:38.26,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,One more piece?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.52,0:02:41.97,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, please. I'll go home after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.70,0:02:45.22,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.22,0:02:46.06,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.62,0:02:49.81,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Um! Something really dramatic.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.49,0:02:55.24,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.64,0:02:58.53,Italics,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.03,0:03:01.78,Italics,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a future that's about to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.74,0:03:06.25,Italics,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,But Kakeru-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.27,0:03:14.14,Italics,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru-kun will be gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.22,0:03:19.26,Main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.34,0:03:24.65,Main,A,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised you all \Nordered Mandheling, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.37,0:03:32.39,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,I'm nervous for some reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.39,0:03:34.27,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I feel weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.92,0:03:43.01,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,It's bitter.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.91,0:03:46.53,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,I wish Touko-san were here, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.53,0:03:50.08,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Remember when the five of us used to\Nget together randomly all the time?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.29,0:03:52.06,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,I'll try calling her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.96,0:03:56.04,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.64,0:03:58.36,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,I want to meet her by chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.55,0:04:01.88,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,That's a nice thing to say \Nfor once, coming from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.14,0:04:03.53,Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,For once, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.79,0:04:11.55,Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I rocked the boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.83,0:04:14.72,Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you both, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.24,0:04:16.52,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.56,0:04:20.49,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone has secrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.70,0:04:24.99,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Well, small ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.25,0:04:28.93,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's because we all \Ngot together for coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.38,0:05:00.70,Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.70,0:05:01.50,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.50,0:05:02.63,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.59,0:05:06.55,Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,Huh, where's Onee-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.41,0:05:08.44,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Dunno.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.44,0:05:10.28,Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,Is she in the studio again so early?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.68,0:05:11.58,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Hina,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.42,0:05:16.60,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,it looks like that girl came home in\Na huge hurry to finish her homework.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.60,0:05:17.81,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get in her way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.23,0:05:19.75,Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.53,0:05:24.54,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Hina, it says there's going \Nto be a meteor shower today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.04,0:05:27.87,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Brings back memories of that night.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.87,0:05:31.13,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Mari said she wanted to \Nwatch the meteor showers,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.13,0:05:33.67,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,so I decided to propose.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.67,0:05:35.86,Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,Dad, move your newspaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.55,0:06:00.62,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.73,0:06:03.56,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,have you decided?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.08,0:06:08.59,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,You're a grown-up, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.59,0:06:13.81,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,You can do whatever you like, \Nand I'll help out as much as I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.59,0:06:17.02,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,It was pretty tough until middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.37,0:06:20.48,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,You're a kid until middle school, \Na grown-up in high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.48,0:06:23.39,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,That's where the line is for me, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.73,0:06:25.84,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,And not for any real reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.46,0:06:28.90,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,So you're still hiking, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.34,0:06:34.82,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, though not so much hiking as \Njust walking around the foothills.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.36,0:06:38.91,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Remember you weren't so enthusiastic \Nabout it when I first invited you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.45,0:06:41.99,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I eventually got into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.99,0:06:44.83,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while since we \Nstopped hiking together.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.83,0:06:47.26,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Can you keep up with me, Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.51,0:06:49.01,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,That's quite a statement.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.36,0:06:52.49,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, dear, come help.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.44,0:06:54.71,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.71,0:06:55.85,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.05,0:06:57.96,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.78,0:06:59.79,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Takayama.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.64,0:07:19.96,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Let's take a short break.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.12,0:07:27.94,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Hina-chan tells me your \Nmom held a piano recital.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.39,0:07:30.06,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't really a recital.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.47,0:07:32.26,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing so grand.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.81,0:07:35.12,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,You should invite me next time, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.56,0:07:36.55,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Takayama, you're—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.55,0:07:37.45,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Yanagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.85,0:07:40.22,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Call me Yanagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.83,0:07:43.27,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Do you like classical music?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.86,0:07:45.44,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I listen to it quite a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.34,0:08:05.27,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Your tea's always so good, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.11,0:08:07.25,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.83,0:08:10.06,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Touko, have you ever
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.06,0:08:14.79,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,seen something in a haze when \Nyou're suddenly in a bright light?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.91,0:08:20.21,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,That'd happen to me sometimes \Nwhen I was young,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.21,0:08:25.52,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,and I even thought it \Nmight have been my future.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.39,0:08:28.78,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,But it wasn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.33,0:08:33.77,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything that happened \Nafterwards was totally unexpected.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.29,0:08:36.65,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what it was, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.38,0:08:40.15,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Does that help you move on?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.31,0:08:45.42,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know, but it's \Nall I can do right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.99,0:08:49.34,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,You're right. You have \Nto do everything you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.24,0:08:59.76,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,You have to fulfill your promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.38,0:09:02.73,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,I'll remind you if you've forgotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.01,0:09:04.30,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,I remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.88,0:09:06.94,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,I've promised you only one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.46,0:09:11.42,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Want to sit?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.42,0:09:12.61,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me later.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.25,0:09:17.71,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,I heard the gist of it from Sachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.60,0:09:20.58,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.58,0:09:23.70,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,The incident at the beach where I was forced
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.70,0:09:26.92,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,to make that promise with you, \Nand this time, when Touko collapsed—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.92,0:09:28.08,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,both are my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.86,0:09:33.45,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,How much of that am I supposed to believe?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.93,0:09:36.31,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard to believe all of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.01,0:09:39.58,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind, but it's the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.58,0:09:43.23,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, it's true that I \Nneeded Touko to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.15,0:09:47.85,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,But if I weren't here, \NTouko wouldn't have gone through all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.27,0:09:49.97,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,I hurt Touko.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.50,0:09:54.15,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,I don't even have a clue what Touko saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.61,0:09:57.32,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,It's not all good,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.24,0:09:59.49,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,coming to an epiphany.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.00,0:10:03.70,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.69,0:10:06.15,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Are you talking about Yukinari Imi?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.73,0:10:09.73,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's about Yuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.34,0:10:14.46,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't need to say anything \Nfor me to know what he's thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.99,0:10:17.47,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that does sound a bit troublesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.50,0:10:19.72,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,So,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.30,0:10:23.35,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru, are you going away?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.39,0:10:26.97,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,I get that feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.72,0:10:30.25,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm heading out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.25,0:10:31.71,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.54,0:10:35.82,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Where's she going this\N late in the afternoon?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.82,0:10:38.41,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know, but she was pretty excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.41,0:10:40.61,Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Onee-chan off to so late?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.98,0:10:44.12,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,My, my, everyone's worried about Onee-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.09,0:11:29.41,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.04,0:11:30.86,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Touko.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.64,0:11:41.30,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Can I sit next to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.73,0:11:42.72,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.21,0:11:53.91,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,There's supposed to be \Na meteor shower tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.55,0:11:56.66,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be great if we can watch it \Nagain, the way we did the fireworks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.10,0:11:59.78,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I hope we can watch the \Nfireworks together again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.03,0:12:02.57,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe not with this weather.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.68,0:12:04.87,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Fireworks in the winter.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.10,0:12:06.99,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,In the winter?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.59,0:12:09.59,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,In the fragment of the future,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.59,0:12:12.12,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,we decided to watch the \Nfireworks in the winter.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.49,0:12:13.45,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,So did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.45,0:12:14.18,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.43,0:12:16.84,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I went alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.84,0:12:17.88,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,And the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.77,0:12:20.81,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,They didn't notice me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.36,0:12:24.34,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,I see, so you watched them alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.79,0:12:28.53,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,It was the first time I ever \Nwatched the fireworks alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.49,0:12:34.35,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,It might have been a sudden, \Nexpected loneliness.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.58,0:12:38.35,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I saw it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.78,0:12:40.45,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,You were watching, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.45,0:12:41.49,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,With the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.32,0:12:44.36,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Did that me seem happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.36,0:12:45.83,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, very.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.37,0:12:47.65,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.99,0:12:52.85,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what the fragments \Nof the future really were.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.27,0:12:56.43,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe that name isn't appropriate anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.12,0:12:59.64,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Mom said—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.32,0:13:01.69,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.88,0:13:08.27,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,There you go with your "never mind" again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.02,0:13:14.43,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,But whenever you say that, \Nit was actually something important.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.07,0:13:18.42,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Am I that obvious?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.42,0:13:19.44,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.01,0:13:21.07,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.74,0:13:22.89,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.89,0:13:24.24,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Something important.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.59,0:13:28.03,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,That day of the fireworks \Nfestival, I saw you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.71,0:13:30.25,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Was that a coincidence?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.25,0:13:31.70,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Not quite.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.36,0:13:33.65,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.30,0:13:37.00,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,You saw it because you wanted to see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.74,0:13:41.75,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.75,0:13:46.01,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's something that hasn't happened, \Nbut it's sure to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.10,0:13:49.78,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,What? Isn't that the same thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.19,0:13:51.85,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Did you mean it to be the same thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.07,0:13:54.27,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe not.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.10,0:13:57.85,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Then it probably means something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.12,0:14:03.33,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.93,0:14:05.63,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.23,0:14:07.86,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,So I saw you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.81,0:14:13.37,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,And the sound and lights from the \Nfireworks might have made it happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.84,0:14:16.15,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,It was really loud and bright, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.62,0:14:18.55,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,But why me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.02,0:14:23.59,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't do anything for you, \Neven during the fireworks in the winter.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.97,0:14:28.13,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I just felt like I understood \Nhow you feel a little better.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.72,0:14:32.75,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't do anything for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.93,0:14:35.64,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.19,0:14:37.63,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,It is?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.90,0:14:41.08,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad I met you in this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.68,0:14:46.34,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad you came to this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.87,0:14:51.60,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Can't see the stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.92,0:14:53.78,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.38,0:14:57.26,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,maybe these will be stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.70,0:15:00.67,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,You made all these?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.67,0:15:01.57,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.25,0:15:03.22,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.79,0:15:33.53,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Ready, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.16,0:15:52.53,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Shooting stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.53,0:15:53.35,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.82,0:15:55.75,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,You see them, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.75,0:15:56.76,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.86,0:16:10.64,Italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,This year's meteor shower \Ncomes unusually late.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.64,0:16:14.53,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,The peak of the Kappa Cygnids meteor \Nshower reaches its peak today;
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.53,0:16:17.47,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,unfortunately there is cloud \Ncover throughout much of Japan,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.47,0:16:18.45,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and it may not be visible—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.57,0:16:21.26,Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.26,0:16:22.63,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.26,0:16:28.42,Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,I can see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.30,0:16:30.51,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,You can?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.32,0:16:48.81,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,It...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.10,0:16:52.04,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,was a beautiful proposal.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.10,0:16:56.63,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,When we first met and when \Nwe went on our first date,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.63,0:16:58.83,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,you were so desperate.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.44,0:17:02.31,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,You won me over.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.47,0:17:33.88,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Why is Jonathan the only Jonathan?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.71,0:17:37.46,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay, Yuki-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.46,0:17:39.81,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,It's still hot outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.81,0:17:41.29,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,No,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.88,0:17:44.67,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, the rest of them all \Nhave philosophers' names.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.52,0:17:48.50,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,What? Then what about Jonathan?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.84,0:17:51.35,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,An adventurer, arguably?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.82,0:17:55.26,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,You've been drawing them all \Nthe time. You didn't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.54,0:17:58.02,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.07,0:18:02.46,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Summer break's almost over.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.92,0:18:07.35,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I hope no matter what happens from now on,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.81,0:18:11.98,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,my future self will solve it all for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.67,0:18:16.53,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't changed at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.37,0:18:20.53,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.37,0:18:49.65,Main,C,0000,0000,0000,,He's back on track lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.84,0:18:51.63,Main,D,0000,0000,0000,,Here he comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.61,0:18:53.29,Main,C,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.29,0:18:54.93,Main,D,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.93,0:18:56.69,Main,A,0000,0000,0000,,It's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.04,0:18:58.42,Main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Hina.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.42,0:18:59.28,Main,C,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Hina?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.29,0:19:02.78,Main,C,0000,0000,0000,,Hina, explain, dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.78,0:19:04.16,Main,D,0000,0000,0000,,Hina!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.30,0:19:17.30,Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,Adjust focus there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.10,0:19:24.03,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,I see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.20,0:19:32.21,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,I like the name Touko.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.08,0:19:33.96,Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.51,0:19:38.22,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,But I love the name Hiro, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.74,0:19:40.74,Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazemichi
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.23,0:19:45.92,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Should I help with something?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.27,0:19:48.66,Main,A,0000,0000,0000,,You're a customer for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.77,0:19:56.02,Main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.02,0:19:58.67,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,You're late.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.89,0:20:18.57,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't she going to be late?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.28,0:20:22.28,Main,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.57,0:20:26.49,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Summer break's over for \Nus youngins, unlike you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.82,0:20:29.16,Main,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,There's something wrong. \NYou didn't sleep in.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.16,0:20:30.97,Main,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,Did something good happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.26,0:20:36.27,Main,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,That tragic glasses girl is coming to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.27,0:20:37.05,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Ack!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.43,0:20:41.40,Main,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,Good for you. I'll give \Nyou a lift to celebrate.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.40,0:20:46.35,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,The only way I'd be late today would\Nbe because you gave me a ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.67,0:20:47.81,Main,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,Tee hee.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.56,0:20:56.44,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,This is another benefit of running, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.39,0:21:12.88,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.88,0:21:14.08,Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,I'm leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.96,0:21:17.63,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Watch for cars, you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.75,0:21:45.57,Italics,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Touko.
